{"data":[{"date":"09:51 02/07","title":"M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \"Pogba Serbia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus quan t\u00e2m Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio, anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-cua-serie-a-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-sao-khung-arsenal-172-189741.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lazio quan t\u00e2m Ramsey</span> c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Lazio-muon-mua-Aaron-Ramsey-thay-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Lazio d\u00e0nh cho Milinkovic-Savic khi\u1ebfn Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo Tuttosport, Lazio \u0111\u00f2i 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rodrigo Bentancur m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, n\u1ebfu Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Juventus g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n MU, PSG v\u00e0 Barca l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3931","checkdouble":"190157"},{"date":"09:55 02/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn CLB c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marlon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarlon t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Marlon Santos da Silva Barbosa, sinh ng\u00e0y 7 th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 1995. Anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona t\u1eeb Fluminense d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Blaugrana k\u00fd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng do kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi Ernesto Valverde, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em Marlon cho Nice c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Fluminense m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNice kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Marlon v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 anh l\u1ea1i Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 Valverde v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Southampton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Marlon c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Barca. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 Southampton v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Blaugrana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Marlon s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Southampton ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marlon s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Southampton h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Stuart Armstrong t\u1eeb Celtic v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Basler Mohamed Elyounoussi t\u1eeb Basel. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Saints \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn Andrea Petagna c\u1ee7a Atalanta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca-172-189954.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot-180-189772.html\">Sao Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich-180-189512.html\">Barca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3930","checkdouble":"190156"},{"date":"10:58 02/07","title":"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/11/real-madrid-da-co-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 BL\u0110 Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Tuong-lai-Luka-Modric-da-duoc-quyet-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn cho Real Madrid, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 theo \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid-180-189278.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Luka Modric</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edd Mirror c\u1ee7a Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 BL\u0110 Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/real-madrid-da-co-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n40 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng si\u00eau l\u00f2ng, nh\u01b0ng Real Madrid th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Real Madrid b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, anh tin r\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Modric v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Modric \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf Nga. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3929","checkdouble":"190162"},{"date":"09:34 02/07","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201ckh\u1eafc tinh\u201d c\u1ee7a Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/barca-muon-mua-kante-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y lu\u00f4n g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Messi. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Messi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17, N'Golo Kante kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. S\u1ee9c c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 qua 2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Barcelona m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 theo k\u00e8m si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi. D\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Leicester, ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Barca-muon-mua-Kante-cua-Chelsea,-khac-tinh-cua-Messi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kante khi\u1ebfn Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y th\u00f4i, khi g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Kante ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Messi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Argentina m\u1ea5t h\u00fat trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Eric Abidal, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. T\u1edd Don Balon cho hay nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Barca bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Lionel Messi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante\" title=\"Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/15/barca-muon-mua-kante-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, Tiki-Taka v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i l\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barca. Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Messi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t ngay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Kante c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf trung tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eeba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Ernesto Valverde, Barca c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 Paulinho v\u00e0 Nelson Semedo cho Blaugrana \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng mua Willian, Barca v\u1eabn b\u1ecb Chelsea kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca-172-189954.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot-180-189772.html\">Sao Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3928","checkdouble":"190155"},{"date":"10:55 02/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i khuy\u00ean Gareth Bale b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng vinh quang m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh M.U v\u00e0 \u0110T x\u1ee9 Wales, Mickey Thomas.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bale mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid, Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1 La Liga v\u00e0 4 Champions League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mong mu\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady. Ngay sau khi c\u00f9ng Real \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 th\u00e1ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBale mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i Real. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 th\u00f4i, Jonathan Barnett - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bale c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham n\u00f3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Gareth-Bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-Real-ve-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bale c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi \u201cC\u01a1n l\u1ed1c x\u1ee9 Wales\u201d bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Bayern Munich c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 Premier League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 M.U v\u00e0 x\u1ee9 Wales: Mickey Thomas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGareth Bale kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 63 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cCV c\u1ee7a Bale \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale\" title=\"Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United, Chelsea r\u1ed3i Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi Gareth Bale. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Thomas tin \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Neymar ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u, Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i cho Bayern Munich, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid-172-189040.html\">Ryan Giggs khuy\u00ean Mourinho k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-united-chuan-bi-dua-gareth-bale-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-172-188500.html\">Man United chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0a Gareth Bale l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u201ckh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-tuong-lai-ronaldo-va-bale-nuong-nhau-ma-song-180-188128.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo v\u00e0 Bale: N\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau m\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/bo-vo-tuong-lai-bi-cam-tham-du-dam-cuoi-cua-bale-188-187786.html\">B\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-moi-goi-gareth-bale-den-old-trafford-172-187570.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3927","checkdouble":"190161"},{"date":"19:46 01/07","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ket-qua-quang-nam-vs-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL: 2-2<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: V\u0103n To\u00e0n (45'+1; 55'); Thanh Trung (73'); Minh Tu\u1ea5n (76')</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHAGL b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau chu\u1ed7i 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng \u2018ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n\u2019 sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-2 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HAGL c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Thanh T\u00f9ng t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t khung th\u00e0nh CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam trong gang t\u1ea5c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Ket-qua-Quang-Nam-vs-HAGL-vong-17-V-League-2018-chieu-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 y\u1ebfu \u1edbt v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd hi\u1ec7p 1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, HAGL c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 55. Sau khi \u0111o\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhanh t\u1eeb trung v\u1ec7 Thiago, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn b\u1edfi t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 73 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau qu\u1ea3 penalty m\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay trung v\u1ec7 Zeba c\u1ee7a HAGL trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, Thanh Trung d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 1-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2. Sau khi b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 b\u1eadt ra tr\u00fang ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 cho CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-2 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 HAGL ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau v\u00f2ng 17.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3926","checkdouble":"190089"},{"date":"19:55 01/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League.</h2><h2>1. C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ghi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u00e0 t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ghi th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng pha ghi b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc song n\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat HAGL. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Toan ghi cu dup ban thang cho HAGL\" title=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;</em><i>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n To\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n ra m\u1eaft CLB HAGL, trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t 11m. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m n\u00e1ch, tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, \u0110inh Thanh Trung \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 1-2 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ngo\u1ea1i binh Josip Zeba v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf HAGL sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 3 ph\u00fat. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ghi th\u00eam v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nan gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi HAGL. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Qu\u1ea3ng Nam g\u1eb7p may<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t n\u00e0y m\u00e0 may m\u1eafn song h\u00e0nh, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha th\u1ed5i penalty c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ch\u1ec9 2 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n. T\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Huy H\u00f9ng, b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m x\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh HAGL r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eadp l\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Minh Tu\u1ea5n c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Qu\u1ea3ng Nam may m\u1eafn gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t HAGL \u0111ang h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 17\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 17\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-17.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 5 tr\u00ean BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 17</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 5 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 2 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau khi Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u0169ng b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 22 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 17 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 8. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp sau v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1 v\u00e0 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9, vi\u1ec7c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ket-qua-quang-nam-vs-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay HAGL?</span><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb CLB HAGL thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i V-League. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu-168-189946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu-168-189946.html\">HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL \u0111ang th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh th\u1ee9 hai cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a V-League 2018 mang t\u00ean Josip Zeba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Croatia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3925","checkdouble":"190109"},{"date":"05:20 02/07","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, HLV U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.</h2><h2>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ef5 d\u01a1 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 \u0111em sang Indonesia \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/dsc00001-0142.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc: \u201cH\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc v\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1eafng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng sai s\u1ed1 trong d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Phlippines. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 15h30, ng\u00e0y 03/07.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-325-190103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-325-190103.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (Gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nNgay l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17-372-190078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17-372-190078.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (KT): Phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3924","checkdouble":"190139"},{"date":"05:52 02/07","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ec3 thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ec3 thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-VAN-SY2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb &nbsp;\u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 17 V-League b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 &lsquo;nh\u1ea1t&rsquo;. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 tranh ch\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft c\u00f2i nh\u01b0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 h\u01a1i \u00e1c&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, d\u00f9 t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n Phong c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m vui sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n thay HLV ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho t\u00e2m l\u00ed anh em c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch c\u1edfi b\u1ecf t\u00e2m l\u00ed, ch\u01a1i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3923","checkdouble":"190140"},{"date":"19:19 01/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/7: Kroos b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/23/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-17-kroos-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/7.</h2><h2>Juventus nh\u1eafm si\u00eau sao Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Juventus h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bernabeu khi kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 31.5 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Real. C\u1ea3 PSG v\u00e0 Man United c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Anthony Martial. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Franck Ribery v\u00e0 Arjen Robben \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. V\u00e0 Martial \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean l\u00e0m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria.</div>\r\n<h2>Kroos t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17 Kroos b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17 Kroos b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/11/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-17-Kroos-bao-tin-buon-cho-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/7:\u00a0Kroos t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Man United h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kroos mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Bernabeu t\u1edbi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022. Kroos tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i Man City.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u1ee5 Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Mail \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma. The Blues nh\u1eafm Alisson nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Courtois, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp s\u1eeda chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Uruguay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, Arsenal \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lucas Torreira</span>. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n s\u00e2n Emirates. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Arsenal ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sau khi World Cup kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Uruguay s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6/7 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Karius v\u1eabn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Sun, Loris Karius d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, l\u00fd do l\u00e0 ph\u00eda Roma \u0111\u00f2i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. Vi\u1ec7c Jack Butland l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Stoke khi\u1ebfn Liverpool kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o Karius \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-306-tro-cung-mourinho-bat-ngo-o-lai-mu-184-189977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/6: Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-296-mu-muon-chieu-mo-sao-tuyen-duc-chelsea-sap-co-bom-tan-184-189959.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/6: M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3922","checkdouble":"190106"},{"date":"21:35 01/07","title":"R\u1eddi World Cup 2018, Ronaldo s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/roi-world-cup-2018-ronaldo-sap-co-ben-do-moi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><h2>Ronaldo chia tay Real sau World Cup?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1eddi World Cup 2018, Ronaldo chia tay Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1eddi World Cup 2018, Ronaldo chia tay Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Roi-World-Cup-2018,-Ronaldo-chia-tay-Real-de-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo sau khi anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i du l\u1ecbch ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn CR7 c\u0169ng \u0111ang ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real l\u00e0 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 619.000 b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Neymar. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 1,35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n.V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ronaldo chia tay Real c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd b\u00e1o ti\u1ebfng \u00dd Tuttosport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00ec Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi m\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y CLB Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xu\u1ed1ng 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (kho\u1ea3ng 130 tri\u1ec7u USD). Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real t\u1eebng treo gi\u00e1 884 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\u00a0cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ronaldo.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tan-man/bong-da-tro-choi-cua-tap-the-392-190025.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/bong-da-tro-choi-cua-tap-the.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tan-man/bong-da-tro-choi-cua-tap-the-392-190025.html\">Messi - Ronaldo: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 - tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, m\u1ecdi con m\u1eaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o hai si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u hay ho kh\u00e1c....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/santos.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\">Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\nFernando Santos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 63 tu\u1ed5i hy v\u1ecdng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Seleccao thay v\u00ec chia tay \u0110TQG.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket-421-190050.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket-421-190050.html\">NHM r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span><br>\r\nGary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh NHM s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3921","checkdouble":"190117"},{"date":"18:02 01/07","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u1ea1nh tranh sao s\u00e1ng World Cup c\u00f9ng Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tottenham-muon-mua-quintero-cung-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quintero g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf Porto, Juan Quintero \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho River Plate c\u1ee7a Argentina m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Colombia v\u00e0 Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i River, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Quintero \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed3i sinh. Anh d\u1ea7n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Colombia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/tottenham-muon-mua-quintero-cung-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, Quintero \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Ba Lan hay Senegal \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh t\u1ea1i Medellin, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 2 Colombia \u0111\u1ec1u tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Quintero t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. Sau Real Madrid, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho Harry Kane, Spurs mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Porto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Quintero kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Tottenham hay Real. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi River c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro theo nh\u01b0 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Quintero l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, song h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ebfm l\u1eddi t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Quintero, nghe \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o River s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh r\u1ed3i b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Anh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, con s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f2n t\u0103ng l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc-172-189950.html\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1ee5 Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-tien-dao-la-172-189945.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ea1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic-180-189349.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid-180-189278.html\">Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3920","checkdouble":"190101"},{"date":"22:11 01/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/24/nong-arsenal-sap-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, CLB Arsenal \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 ba mang t\u00ean Sokratis Papastathopoulos sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Anh.</h2><h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sokratis Papastathopoulos\u00a0</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB Arsenal \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos t\u1eeb CLB Borussia Dortmund.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Sokratis Papastathopoulos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Sokratis Papastathopoulos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/11/Nong-Arsenal-sap-co-tan-binh-Sokratis-Papastathopoulos-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Arsenal \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u00e0n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Sokratis Papastathopoulos</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, khi \u1ea5y c\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp, Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 192 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Dortmund v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn bao g\u1ed3m Arsenal v\u00e0 c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Manchester United, Juventus hay Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Dortmund, Papastathopoulos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng-\u0111en \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1ea3 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba Arsenal mua sao Dortmund, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Sven Mislintat v\u00e0 Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh, Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn London t\u1eeb\u00a0 Kalamata, Hy L\u1ea1p v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y l\u00fac 7h t\u1ed1i (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng). Anh ta c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 cha m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 Ba c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Bernd Leno.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-172-190091.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-172-190091.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nArsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\">Neville khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Lucas Torreira sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia-172-189966.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia-172-189966.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Colombia</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3919","checkdouble":"190121"}]}